<div class="hidden-content control-hide">
<p class="ql-align-center">如果那只叫流浪者的狗不叫，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">Mama's gonna buy you a horse and cart.</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">妈妈会去给你买一辆马车。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">If that horse and cart fall down,</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">如果马车倒了，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">You'll be the sweetest little baby in town.</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">你就成为镇上最甜蜜的小宝贝了。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">So hush little baby don’t you cry,</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">所以，安静啦，宝贝不哭了，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">Daddy loves you and so do I.</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">爸爸爱你，妈妈也爱你。</p>
